Class Gomoku

java.lang.Object
java.util.concurrent.SubmissionPublisher<Gomoku>
domain.Gomoku
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, AutoCloseable, Runnable, Flow.Publisher<Gomoku>
public class Gomoku extends SubmissionPublisher<Gomoku> implements Runnable, Serializable
The Gomoku class represents a game of Gomoku, a two-player strategy board game. It manages the game state, player information, and provides access to various aspects of the ongoing Gomoku game.
Version:
1.8.5
Author:
Juan Daniel Murcia - Mateo Forero Fuentes
